AYERS
v.
CLEVELAND 2018-0852 Supreme Court of Ohio. August 31, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

On motions for admission pro hac vice of Russell Ainsworth, Ruth Brown, and Michael Kanovitz. Motions denied. The attorneys are stricken from the case. On appellees' motion to strike notice of appeal and memoranda in support of jurisdiction. Motion denied as moot.
